<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT8">
<l>ilaituṇaimaṟ ṟeṉṉeñcē yīcaṉai veṉṟa</l>
<l>cilaikoṇṭa ceṅkaṇmāṟ cērā kulaikoṇṭa</l>
<l>vīrain talaiyā ṉilaṅkaiyai yīṭaḻitta</l>
<l>kūrampa ṉallāṟ kuṟai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O my heart! [In times of] need, there is no companion other than</l>
<l>the red-eyed Māl with a bow that defeated Śiva,</l>
<l>Him with sharp arrows that destroyed the might of the Laṅkā</l>
<l rend="indent">of [Rāvaṇa] with a cluster of ten heads, who did not reach [Rāma].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
